;m not using CDN, I delete all cache folder about w3 total cache and generate a new .htaccess but nothing change. I don&#8217;t have any other cache plugin too.</p>\n<p>I&#8217;m using Savoy theme. </p>\n<p>If I look for network requests when page load the fonts from fonts.gstatic.com are with BLOCKED status.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://paste.pics/CQYDQ\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://paste.pics/CQYDQ</a></p>\n<p>Thank you</p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/W3TOTALCACHE/~4/GipA0cpJXk0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"joaot\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"https://wordpress.org/support/topic/after-uninstall-lose-icons/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:25;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:150:\"&lt;span class=&quot;resolved&quot; aria-label=&quot;Resolved&quot; title=&quot;Topic is resolved.&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;Minify is rewriting font URLs\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:59:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/W3TOTALCACHE/~3/2PBd-3FiIJs/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"Mon, 07 Jun 2021 15:04:30 PDT\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://wordpress.org/support/topic/minify-is-rewriting-font-urls/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1700:\"<p>Replies: 2</p>\n						<p>I was searching for this problem and found this post which I think is describing the exact same issue (<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/topic/minify-css-makes-font-missing/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://wordpress.org/support/topic/minify-css-makes-font-missing/</a>)</p>\n<p>I don&#8217;t think I changed anything, but all of a sudden all of my fonts were having issues. I think the problem is that they were being stored with relative paths, such as:<br />\n<code>src:url(../webfonts/fa-brands-400.eot)</code></p>\n<p>Because the minified version of the CSS will be in a completely different location this means that the web browser will try to open <a href=\"https://mysite.com/wp-content/cache/webfonts/fa-brands-400.eot\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://mysite.com/wp-content/cache/webfonts/fa-brands-400.eot</a> which of course it won&#8217;t find.</p>\n<p>I suspect this might be a recent change in the way in which the Font Awesome css has been updated through Elementor. But aside from this, I was wondering if there is any way your plugin could account for re-writing the URLs so they will resolve correctly?</p>\n<p>I have tried both combine only and combine+minify but both options have this issue.</p>\n<p>I am using NGINX and this .conf was created by your plugin and is included in my config.</p>\n<pre><code># BEGIN W3TC Minify cache\n# END W3TC Minify cache\n# BEGIN W3TC Minify core\nset $w3tc_enc &quot;&quot;;\nif (-f $request_filename$w3tc_enc) {\n    rewrite (.*) $1$w3tc_enc break;\n}\nrewrite ^/wp-content/cache/minify/ /index.php last;\n# END W3TC Minify core</code></pre><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/W3TOTALCACHE/~4/2PBd-3FiIJs\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"mjb2000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://wordpress.org/support/topic/minify-is-rewriting-font-urls/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:26;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:173:\"&lt;span class=&quot;resolved&quot; aria-label=&quot;Resolved&quot; title=&quot;Topic is resolved.&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;What is the benefit of minify Inline JS/CSS in HTML?\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:59:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/W3TOTALCACHE/~3/VRjOeV5RMrs/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"Mon, 07 Jun 2021 09:12:15 PDT\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:88:\"https://wordpress.org/support/topic/what-is-the-benefit-of-minify-inline-js-css-in-html/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:399:\"<p>Replies: 1</p>\n						<p>Hello, </p>\n<p>What is the benefit or the uses of HTML inline minification for CSS and JS?</p>\n<p>I notice that it breaks a few functions but I would love to know it&#8217;s use or benefit. Can&#8217;t find a documentation that explains it&#8217;s use. </p>\n<p>Regards </p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/W3TOTALCACHE/~4/VRjOeV5RMrs\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"essaund\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:88:\"https://wordpress.org/support/topic/what-is-the-benefit-of-minify-inline-js-css-in-html/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:27;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:136:\"&lt;span class=&quot;resolved&quot; aria-label=&quot;Resolved&quot; title=&quot;Topic is resolved.&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;Enabling HTTP/2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:59:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/W3TOTALCACHE/~3/FIjPURyKJaM/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"Mon, 07 Jun 2021 07:51:48 PDT\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"https://wordpress.org/support/topic/enabling-http-2/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\